{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8d9bd03bd6","title":"关于不要“开快车”的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8e8fbe1044","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":13,"articleId":"8d9bd03bd6"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1d593d7bf3","type":"title","text":"关于不要“开快车”的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8d9bd03bd6"},{"id":"70cf60d457","type":"paragraph","text":"开快车要翻车，要打招呼。当前主要搞大联合、三结合，环人挖出来，牛鬼蛇神挖出来。党组织要恢复，各级党代表大会召开，人民代表大会召开，我看大体要到明年这个时候，大家不要有疲劳的感觉，不要想脱身。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8d9bd03bd6"}],"page":{"id":"983f8df4c2","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8d9bd03bd6","start":541,"end":541}}}},"__N_SSG":true}